00:00:00.310 --> 00:00:03.090
A great place to start when
researching your distribution plan

00:00:03.090 --> 00:00:04.580
is through Google Trends.

00:00:04.580 --> 00:00:07.220
Google Trends is
a completely free service

00:00:07.220 --> 00:00:10.340
that allows you to see
the popularity of search terms

00:00:10.340 --> 00:00:14.140
in relation to the total volume
of search terms across the world.

00:00:14.140 --> 00:00:15.650
And in various languages.

00:00:15.650 --> 00:00:19.952
Google processes over 40,000 search
queries every single second, and

00:00:19.952 --> 00:00:23.270
they're willing to share
those insights with you.

00:00:23.270 --> 00:00:26.550
The reason why this is a great place to
start is that not only can you see some

00:00:26.550 --> 00:00:29.970
really interesting things from
all of these search queries,

00:00:29.970 --> 00:00:32.479
like the most searched topic of the day.

00:00:32.479 --> 00:00:35.660
But you can also see the history
of these search terms and

00:00:35.660 --> 00:00:37.240
of related terms for your business.

00:00:37.240 --> 00:00:38.910
So I have Ronnie here with me,

00:00:38.910 --> 00:00:42.140
