although I see that there are some big-
&gt;&gt; Yeah, that's interesting.

00:00:58.760 --> 00:01:00.640
&gt;&gt; If you look at the dates, yeah,

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:03.760
you can see that there
is a peak every summer.

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:04.470
&gt;&gt; Oh yeah.

00:01:04.470 --> 00:01:08.740
&gt;&gt; So people are searching more for pet
sitting during their summer vacations.

